normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去左40日左右<br />\n我係去到外蒙先坐西伯利亞，咁平好多<br />\n上海-北京-外蒙-奧爾洪島-莫斯科-塔林-聖彼得堡-香港<br />\n杯麵連續食三餐已經想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪即係買火車票到外蒙，之後係蒙古玩幾日，再買西伯利亞火車票上莫斯科咁樣？ 我都有上網睇過人話分段平好多，但係分段係火車就咁補飛，定去到票換車再買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想落埋歐洲玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566c86117d8d776e5ec66d23289d478b0fc103c9","tid":90413,"uid":25052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:45:23.000Z","msg":"我係去到二連補錢買票去蒙古<br />\n咁已經比左一半<br />\n跟住蒙古一早叫左住果度幫手買西伯利亞票<br />\n我都想去埋歐洲但冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a78aa13e31711cf958d24a5d9016442a09316782","tid":90413,"uid":37565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:55:01.000Z","msg":"一齊 okay"},{"pid":"91804b1ce30e0198b0bc0886135257d68bc2079f","tid":90413,"uid":20458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係去到二連補錢買票去蒙古<br />\n咁已經比左一半<br />\n跟住蒙古一早叫左住果度幫手買西伯利亞票<br />\n我都想去埋歐洲但冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗左幾多錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食多幾餐杯面咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02157c44f179fb4c44435345c8abb19052d8d0e","tid":90413,"uid":25052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係去到二連補錢買票去蒙古<br />\n咁已經比左一半<br />\n跟住蒙古一早叫左住果度幫手買西伯利亞票<br />\n我都想去埋歐洲但冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗左幾多錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食多幾餐杯面咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我窮遊包哂全部野二萬有找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會食到想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011d3aebddf337b50fedd3d44fed09df88bcce63","tid":90413,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"分段三千左右就得<br />\n香港&gt;北京&gt;內蒙&gt;外蒙&gt;俄羅斯<br />\n通常都係搭東歐玩<br />\n遲d白俄好似免簽，可以順面去"},{"pid":"c7022d0bcbd8ed4abf045380ed9f2bb8aeec2bfb","tid":90413,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網睇 坐火車去好似要成萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n分段就平d <br />\n有冇人分享下你地車飛要幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n海參崴到莫斯科，最平一千左右。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/10g9uoap\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F10g9uoap&h=5fee0c4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeda5c1c64014fd62f83039966227e17ff07cea2","tid":90413,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T18:02:17.000Z","msg":"Baltic states真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5010883fab04154c73af294600b5a8527423703f","tid":90413,"uid":53981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T19:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係去到二連補錢買票去蒙古<br />\n咁已經比左一半<br />\n跟住蒙古一早叫左住果度幫手買西伯利亞票<br />\n我都想去埋歐洲但冇咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗左幾多錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食多幾餐杯面咪有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買舊包買條腸買啲青瓜蕃茄整三文冶其實都好平 我Irkutsk去Moscow個程就係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋停大站通常都有人賣野 買啲俄餃又一餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}